<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l17">von des vnwıllen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> den der edel <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Jobſt <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ʒu <expan>Abemſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l18">ʒu vns maint ʒu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns geſagt daʒ Jr eẅch gar </ab>
