<ab facs="#facs_86_r1l20"><expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr fürſtenlıch gnade dıenſtlıch </ab>
